	<div class="section-title grey-text text-darken-4 flow-text"><p><strong>WHY SKUM ?</strong></p></div>
</div>
<div class="card-panel row">
	<div class="container about-section">
		<p class="flow-text">Set amidst picturesque 10000 sq. yards campus in the prime location of Ahmedabad, SKUM has spacious classrooms equipped with modern teaching aids.</p>
		<p class="flow-text">SKUM is a leading education group in Ahmedabad with over 1500 students studying in a hi-tech campus. At SKUM, we are passionate about grooming future leaders who are not only thorough professionals, but also good human beings with values and sanskars.</p>
		<p class="flow-text">At SKUM, we pride ourselves for our endeavors. Our faculty and senior team are engaged in teaching and imbibing the students with the best practices so that we can give a solid foundation for learning. As a part of the curriculum, we have hi-technology classrooms that provide the most conductive atmosphere for focused discussions. The libraries at our campus are equipped with books, periodicals, journals and magazines, covering all aspects of academic studies and research material. The well-equipped science laboratory acts as an ideal training ground for budding professionals and allows the students to experiment and bring to practice what they have learnt in theory.</p>
		<p class="flow-text">The team of SKUM comprises of well trained teachers, led by two of the best leaders as principals, guided by a highly motivated director, supported by generous and valued trustees and encouraged by a very enthusiastic staff.</p>
		<p class="flow-text">The school aims at practical academic-oriented teaching; contemporary curriculum updated to keep the students at par with the latest happenings; certificate courses in music, dance, spoken English and Personality Development; values and ethics; art appreciation; making sure of an all round development with sport activities, volleyball, chess, skating, extra curricular activities, exhibitions, competitions, tracking, camps and so on.</p>
		<p class="flow-text">At SKUM, emphasis is given on not only making a child academically brilliant, but also to be true leaders and team players, thus preparing the students for the real life corporate world. At SKUM, counseling services have been set up where expert counselors provide counseling to help students overcome their educational and personal problems.</p>
	</div>
